quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"The Hour draws near; the moon is split in two."
  54,2,"Whenever the disbelievers see a sign, they turn away and say, ‘Same old sorcery!’"
  54,3,"They reject the truth and follow their own desires––everything is recorded––"
  54,4,"although warning tales that should have restrained them have come down to them––"
  54,5,"farreaching wisdom––but these warnings do not help:"
  54,6,"so [Prophet] turn away from them. On the Day the Summoner will summon them to a horrific event,"